description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 2

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014!

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle! 

It's Canberra's turn as newly dating couple and self-titled 'natural entertainers', Andrew and Emelia prepare their three-course menu. Will they create harmony or havoc on the plate?
